{"tid":192472,"cid":34,"subCid":0,"title":"(台測)思·裂 猛鬼追魂1-3","createTime":"2017-04-08T15:21:24.000Z","updateTime":"2017-04-08T20:59:18.000Z","uid":29160,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"c5faf3a2edf98fab3c23d0963ee2a73047044d89","tid":192472,"uid":29160,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-08T15:21:24.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">睇清楚時間幾點播</span><br />\n<a href=\"http://paradiseangel.wixsite.com/thanksyour/about1\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fparadiseangel.wixsite.com%2Fthanksyour%2Fabout1&d=B95HL5QQ1MLE%2FldfuzA7j0%2FDJpISyAq9ELy6OyFxwDc%3D&h=5c79d7fa\" target=\"_blank\">http://paradiseangel.wixsite.com/thanksyour/about1</a> 按右上主頁可以睇返V台<br />\n<a href=\"http://live.sk-knower.com/user/thanksyour?live=vl\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Flive.sk-knower.com%2Fuser%2Fthanksyour%3Flive%3Dvl&d=B95HL5QQ1MLE%2FldfuzA7j0%2FDJpISyAq9ELy6OyFxwDc%3D&h=ca469a63\" target=\"_blank\">http://live.sk-knower.com/user/thanksyour?live=vl</a>可以直接睇到V台<br />\n<img src=\"https://upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/zh/d/df/Split_2017_Poster.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fupload.wikimedia.org%2Fwikipedia%2Fzh%2Fd%2Fdf%2FSplit_2017_Poster.jpg&h=3a133ec0&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"http://img.vice.cn/contentimage/4160/1424842429v9ebl5jobqt23ox5oxpm.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fimg.vice.cn%2Fcontentimage%2F4160%2F1424842429v9ebl5jobqt23ox5oxpm.jpg&h=a6a3bd23&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n1.故事敘述凱文被信任的心理醫生診斷出擁有二十三個人格，但還有一個未知人格尚未覺醒。在眾多人格的競爭下，這也造成他動身綁架了三名十幾歲的少女，以醞釀未知的計劃....<br />\n<br />\n2.賴瑞與第二任妻子茱莉亞(Julia)搬入新家，然而賴瑞卻不知道茱莉亞早與自己的兄弟法蘭克有染，茱莉亞得知情人法蘭克被一個神秘的魔盒殺死，需要人血獻祭才能復活，便開始勾引獵殺無辜的男人，另一方面，賴瑞的女兒克莉絲汀(Kirsty)撿到了魔盒，不小心釋放出「針頭」等地獄修道士們......<br />\n<br />\n3.克莉絲汀進了精神病院，遇到了沉迷於邪術研究的查納德醫生，他不但以人血將邪惡的茱莉亞復活，還利用自閉症女孩蒂芬妮解開魔盒，開啟地獄之門，闖入地獄世界的克莉絲汀與蒂芬妮等人能全身而退嗎.....?<br />\n<br />\n4.女記者喬伊目賭一樁鐵鍊殺人慘案，決心要查出真相，而調查途中又牽扯出了針頭鬼欲復活並且將人間化為地獄的陰謀，眼看針頭大開殺戒，喬伊能阻止他嗎?而不斷出現在喬伊夢中的神秘男子艾略特．史賓賽將會是打敗針頭的關鍵...?<br />\n<br />\n11 30PM左右播了 隨時電腦大爆炸<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/yipes.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"95f3f49e988e8a2cdef39e0181eb85085e7ae38f","tid":192472,"uid":29160,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-08T15:22:48.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1007ef08ed06b0a55bdd66948f09ae9f57c29341","tid":192472,"uid":29160,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-08T15:33:48.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e110d687a9dcf9922650660f51bcd52158b5579b","tid":192472,"uid":29160,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-08T15:53:22.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/photo.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/photo.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4163868a370652ff3444088abd9eef594e70c4f1","tid":192472,"uid":29160,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-08T16:16:03.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/z.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/z.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"155bd5aaafe6835253df7363d726052241e9223d","tid":192472,"uid":29160,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-08T16:47:33.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bc89d11085c9a17bbe954a356c6dd4c8ecdfd68c","tid":192472,"uid":29160,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-08T17:29:54.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/z.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/z.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"34abc73126dccc3e02db51c9b97deca4c0fa6f66","tid":192472,"uid":29160,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":